These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, train, trike, ship, quad-bike
House: tower, ranch-style, farmhouse, palace, craftsman
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
The people have 5 different jobs:  social-worker, designer, scientist, fisherman, software-developer
 1. the scientist is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the software-developer is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 3. the designer is on the right of the tower house##1
 4. the social-worker is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the palace house##1
 6. the ranch-style house is the person driving the train##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
10. the person driving the ship is on the left of the social-worker##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the social-worker##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Transport         | train  | helicopter    | ship | trike    | quad-bike  |
| House   | ranch-style  | tower | farmhouse | palace | craftsman  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| Job         | scientist | fisherman    | designer | social-worker  | software-developer |

