.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, kiwi, lettuce, watermelon
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy, daisy, aconite, orchid
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ebony, turquise, blood-red, chestnut
5 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, ferret, cat, frog
 1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is the person who likes ebony##1
 3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
 5. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is the person who likes turquise##1
 9. the owner of the cat is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
12. the person eating kiwi is the person who growspoppy##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi        | watermelon | cucumber     | lettuce      | artichoke  |
| Flower           | poppy   | daisy | orchid    | aconite | azalea |
| Color   | turquise | blood-red     | chestnut | fuchsia    | ebony  |
| Pet   | cat     | goldfish | goat    | frog      | ferret    |

