.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: punk, gospel, salsa, classical, folk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, zombie, fantasy, comedy, adventure
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, game, vegafina, havana, chaman
 1. the fan of classical is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 3. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
 7. the havana-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the chaman-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the person watching fantasy movies is the fan of punk##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| Music-Genre         | gospel | folk | classical  | salsa   | punk    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie        | adventure | documentary | comedy    | fantasy   |
| Cigar     | fonseca   | vegafina | chaman      | game | havana |

