 3. the chinese is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the polish is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the german##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
 9. the german is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person eating zucchini is the malaysian##1
11. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the owner of the bird is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food          | plum        | kale       | papaya | lemon   | zucchini  |
| Sport   | lacrosse | soccer | swimming | basketball   | surfing |
