 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
10. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
11. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fan of funk##1
12. the polish is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Movie-Genre          | fantasy    | adventure  | spy | horror    | crime      |
