.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, azalea, zinnia, dahlia
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, nurse, social-worker, analyst, fisherman
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, house, reggae
5 different games are played: snooker, whist, domino, scrabble, backgammon
 1. the nurse is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 2. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
 3. the analyst is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the person playing whist is on the left of the fan of country##1
 5. the manager is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 7. the nurse is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the manager##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the fisherman##1
12. the social-worker is the fan of house##1
13. the fisherman is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Flower      | poppy      | sunflower       | dahlia         | zinnia  | azalea |
| Job   | social-worker  | analyst | nurse | manager  | fisherman  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | country    | blues        | reggae | folk     |
| Game           | whist | domino      | snooker       | scrabble   | backgammon   |

