.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, aristoff, davidoff, dunhill, cain
The people use 5 different means of transport: train, ship, scooter, trike, car
There are 5 different favourite colors: green, coral, lilac, mauve, emerald
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, sailing, swimming, volleyball
 1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the cain-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is the person driving the ship##1
 9. the person who likes coral is in the middle##1
10. the person who likes green is the person driving the car##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
12. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
13. the dunhill-smoker is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Cigar   | aristoff      | dunhill | davidoff  | cain    | montecristo |
| Transport   | trike     | car     | ship | train      | scooter      |
| Color           | lilac       | green     | coral     | emerald     | mauve   |
| Sport         | basketball | swimming | rowing  | volleyball | sailing   |

