There are 5 different nationalities: italian, russian, brazilian, spanish, french
5 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, rabbit, turtle
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, tulip, orchid, marigold
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 3. the french is the person who growsazalea##1
 4. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsamaryllis is the person watching horror movies##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the person watching action movies is on the left of the russian##1
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 9. the person who growsazalea is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
11. the italian is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
12. the brazilian is the person watching family movies##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
