 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is the british##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
12. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
13. the argentine is the person watching crime movies##1
14. the polish is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
